{"tid":749942,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"人仔台出律師信 唔理會點","createTime":"2018-07-20T12:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T16:47:56.000Z","uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8dc52ed6e206d81b0ee3880fa0d25073aa50578","tid":749942,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"人仔垃圾到唔撚想用 即刻違約轉台 之後sd左張律師信黎話唔交果千零蚊會採取有關法律行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就真係唔撚想比錢呢間垃圾 千零蚊係咪大可以唔理等佢黑名單我算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5342922a42d32f576bd495e90f07eb59808177ae","tid":749942,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"會坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c05ad706d9cab7f633f332a67661fa4a5328fa","tid":749942,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5342922a42d32f576bd495e90f07eb59808177ae","tid":749942,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"會坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:54:49.000Z","msg":"好驚會終身監禁 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2a031520baaa032409f5faa4275ccc260a1e65","tid":749942,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19c05ad706d9cab7f633f332a67661fa4a5328fa","tid":749942,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5342922a42d32f576bd495e90f07eb59808177ae","tid":749942,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"會坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:54:49.000Z","msg":"好驚會終身監禁 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"畀返double佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a42dcab37eff4b407b10246b600e02d8a1fa59","tid":749942,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"認真答：<br />\n你可以唔理，但大約幾個月後會再寄嚟話已將你欠單交由某財務公司處理<br />\n再過幾個月內間財務公司寄信嚟已接納某電信公司授權追數<br />\n再每個月左寄信嚟，直到有人上門追數。當然收數佬唔會好似以前咁淋紅油寫大字，最多上嚟啪下你門，大叫下你個名咁<br />\n又當然你可以唔開門或報下警，但煩到隔離鄰舍就唔係咁好。差佬上到嚟最多同你講「你快啲交咗佢啦，仆街」。（其實都係同你講合法性追數，我哋（差佬）幫你唔到，最多幫你記錄下就算）<br />\n騷擾你一段時間又靜過一排，可能幾個月，又可能一兩年咁又嚟騷擾你<br />\n<br />\n利申：有家人試過，但條友早已唔係屋企住又玩失蹤，騷擾咗家人幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a916911582dfcb504be80ac9488486c6952998","tid":749942,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"漏咗講：由千零蚊加埋息加埋要交3萬幾（好似係），兩年時間內左右嘅息"},{"pid":"842a9cacb6e670f4479110c6148e906bd124d017","tid":749942,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1a916911582dfcb504be80ac9488486c6952998","tid":749942,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"漏咗講：由千零蚊加埋息加埋要交3萬幾（好似係），兩年時間內左右嘅息"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"電話費交乜春息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37c859dfefced6aaa68b56368766517f0d608e2","tid":749942,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842a9cacb6e670f4479110c6148e906bd124d017","tid":749942,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1a916911582dfcb504be80ac9488486c6952998","tid":749942,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"漏咗講：由千零蚊加